ull,\"query_source\":null,\"dream_mode\":null,\"unread\":true,\"query_count\":1,\"search_focus\":\"internet\",\"sources\":[\"web\"],\"featured_images\":[],\"read_write_token\":\"0856a626-553b-46c5-941e-675c7135ffcc\",\"total_threads\":99,\"social_info\":{\"view_count\":0,\"fork_count\":0,\"like_count\":0,\"user_likes\":false},\"assets\":[],\"num_assets\":0,\"attachments\":[]},{\"thread_number\":2,\"last_query_datetime\":\"2026-05-29T11:59:09.941583\",\"mode\":\"copilot\",\"context_uuid\":\"8880faa8-ae4e-4471-ac22-ad1304c667d4\",\"uuid\":\"d6b7f6b4-725d-4b26-82f0-0a1c66c9d635\",\"frontend_uuid\":\"bcd5799c-c451-440f-ab9f-bfd8ec628a4e\",\"frontend_context_uuid\":\"f43d856d-f428-48fe-9d3d-f503f39431dc\",\"slug\":\"d6b7f6b4-725d-4b26-82f0-0a1c66c9d635\",\"title\":\"What is rust programming language\",\"query_str\":\"What is rust programming language\",\"first_answer\":\"{\\\"answer\\\":\\\"Rust is a modern programming language designed for performance, reliability, and memory safety. It is especially known for preventing many bugs at compile time through its ownership and borrowing system, and it does not use a garbage collector.\\\\nRust is popular for systems programming, command-line tools, web services, embedded software, and other performance-sensitive applications. Its tooling...\\\"}\",\"answer_preview\":\"Rust is a modern programming language designed for performance, reliability, and memory safety. It is especially known for preventing many bugs at compile time through its ownership and borrowing system, and it does not use a garbage collector.\\nRust is popular for systems programming, command-line tools, web services, embedded software, and other performance-sensitive applications. Its tooling...\",\"thread_access\":1,\"has_next_page\":true,\"status\":\"COMPLETED\",\"display_model\":\"claude45sonnet\",\"expiry_time\":null,\"source\":\"default\",\"source_metadata\":null,\"thread_status\":\"completed\",\"thread_status_summary\":null,\"thread_status_summary_enum\":null,\"locked_reason\":null,\"wake_at\":null,\"crons\":null,\"stream_created_at\":null,\"persona_id\":null,\"query_source\":null,\"dream_mode\":null,\"unread\":true,\"query_count\":1,\"search_focus\":\"internet\",\"sources\":[\"web\"],\"featured_images\":[],\"read_write_token\":\"4260d4d9-078b-4bf7-ae7f-904f3036e3a7\",\"total_threads\":99,\"social_info\":{\"view_count\":0,\"fork_count\":0,\"like_count\":0,\"user_likes\":false},\"assets\":[],\"num_assets\":0,\"attachments\":[]},{\"thread_number\":3,\"last_query_datetime\":\"2026-05-29T11:58:44.983455\",\"mode\":\"copilot\",\"context_uuid\":\"6a00c168-b24a-495c-adc0-041833169d33\",\"uuid\":\"243c52f4-9774-4d00-9b60-d3a3e5f5294c\",\"frontend_uuid\":\"2d677e49-0f89-4ee4-941d-0d37fd5dfdaa\",\"frontend_context_uuid\":\"e7fe1737-7c04-4a96-b8b7-355fef43348f\",\"slug\":\"243c52f4-9774-4d00-9b60-d3a3e5f5294c\",\"title\":\"Prove sqrt(2) is irrational\",\"query_str\":\"Prove sqrt(2) is irrational\",\"first_answer\":\"{\\\"answer\\\":\\\"Assume \\\\\\\\sqrt{2} is rational, so \\\\\\\\sqrt{2}=\\\\\\\\frac{a}{b} for integers a,b with no common factor and b\\\\\\\\neq 0. Squaring gives 2=\\\\\\\\frac{a^2}{b^2}, so a^2=2b^2, which means a^2 is even, and therefore a must be even.\\\\n\\\\nSo write a=2k for some integer k. Substituting back gives (2k)^2=2b^2, hence 4k^2=2b^2, so b^2=2k^2; thus b^2 is even, and therefore b is even too.\\\\n\\\\nBut now both a and b are even, so they...\\\"}\",\"answer_preview\":\"Assume \\\\sqrt{2} is rational, so \\\\sqrt{2}=\\\\frac{a}{b} for integers a,b with no common factor and b\\\\neq 0. Squaring gives 2=\\\\frac{a^2}{b^2}, so a^2=2b^2, which means a^2 is even, and therefore a must be even.\\n\\nSo write a=2k for some integer k. Substituting back gives (2k)^2=2b^2, hence 4k^2=2b^2, so b^2=2k^2; thus b^2 is even, and therefore b is even too.\\n\\nBut now both a and b are even, so they...\",\"thread_access\":1,\"has_next_page\":true,\"status\":\"COMPLETED\",\"display_model\":\"o3mini\",\"expiry